<p><strong><a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/scp-4804">SCP-4804</a> - The Pulp is Fictional (JamCon 2019 Entry) - Rating: +219</strong><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><em>In cases where subjects begin to believe oranges are works of fiction&#8230; they will actively deny the existence of oranges, citing beliefs such as the belief that oranges are simply a variant of apples, oranges being a government conspiracy, and not being able to perceive any orange-related products at all.</em></p>
