<p><strong><a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/not-a-seagull-proposal">SCP-001</a> - The Sky above the Port (JamCon 2019 Entry) - Rating: +404</strong><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><em>[King/Prince/loved one], it is time for you to wake up.</em></p>
