    </div><div class="list-pages-box">    <div class="list-pages-item">


<p><strong><a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/scp-4688">SCP-4688</a> - Manipulative Bike Helmets (CollabCon 2019 Entry) - Rating: +149</strong> - Documentation filed with the assistance of <a href="http://www.scp-wiki.net/dr-mews-personnel-file">Dr. Mew</a><br />
<span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><em>those helmets have been really cool with helping get my friends to get me more friends, but sometimes these friends complain i was hoping as the little genius you were you had something else to help like another toy? :)</em></p>
